  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "If approved by the voters of the state at the 2026 general election, the concurrent resolution authorizes a county to allow an exemption from property tax imposed by the county to the owner-occupier of single-family residential real property owned outright by the owner-occupier without a mortgage.(Note: This summary applies to this concurrent resolution as introduced.)"
    }
  ],
